spec:
assets:
  v1:
  - inline:
      contents: |
        apiVersion: apps/v1
        kind: Deployment
        metadata:
          name: redis
          labels:
            component: redis
        spec:
          replicas: 1
          selector:
            matchLabels:
              component: redis
          template:
            metadata:
              labels:
                component: redis
            spec:
              containers:
                - name: redis
                  image: redis
                  args: ["--appendonly", "yes"]
      dest: base/redis-deployment.yaml
      mode: 0644
config:
  v1: []
lifecycle:
  v1:
  - config:
      invalidates: ["render"]
  - render:
      requires: ["config"]
      root: "."
  - kustomize:
      requires: ["render"]
      base: ./base
      overlay: overlays/ship
      dest: rendered.yaml
